SYSTEM: Sparqlex.pdf: Página 12
Queries about the instances
• Give me the label of all the places that have
more than 200.000 inhabitant
PREFIX pr: <http://GP-onto.fi.upm.es/Practica2#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?x ?y  WHERE { $place pr:NumeroHabitantes ?y;
rdfs:label ?x.
FILTER(?y > 200000) }
speaker: SYSTEM
